DefaultReaderConfiguration.idQuery: SELECT MAX(vfe.event_id) FROM (SELECT dbo.ev_event.event_id FROM dbo.ev_event LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves ON dbo.ev_event.hostname = dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.strName LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.ev_param ON dbo.ev_event.event_id = dbo.ev_param.event_id) AS vfe
DefaultReaderConfiguration.preQueryCheck: SELECT COUNT(vfe.event_id) FROM (SELECT dbo.ev_event.event_id FROM dbo.ev_event LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves ON dbo.ev_event.hostname = dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.strName LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.ev_param ON dbo.ev_event.event_id = dbo.ev_param.event_id) AS vfe WHERE event_id > ?
DefaultReaderConfiguration.queryString: SELECT registration_time, event_id, host_winhostname, group_name, event_type, event_type_display_name, GNRL_EA_DESCRIPTION, GNRL_EA_PARAM_1, GNRL_EA_PARAM_2, GNRL_EA_PARAM_3, GNRL_EA_PARAM_4, GNRL_EA_PARAM_5, GNRL_EA_PARAM_6, GNRL_EA_PARAM_7, GNRL_EA_PARAM_8, GNRL_EA_PARAM_9, task_new_state, task_old_state, task_display_name FROM (SELECT dbo.ev_event.event_id, dbo.ev_event.severity AS GNRL_EA_SEVERITY, dbo.ev_event.origin_is_policy, dbo.ev_event.task_id, dbo.ev_event.group_name, dbo.ev_event.hostname, dbo.ev_event.product_name, dbo.ev_event.product_version, dbo.ev_event.product_displ_version, dbo.ev_event.event_type, dbo.ev_event.event_type_display_name, dbo.ev_event.descr AS GNRL_EA_DESCRIPTION, dbo.ev_event.rise_time, dbo.ev_event.deadline, dbo.ev_event.body, dbo.ev_param.par1 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_1, dbo.ev_param.par2 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_2, dbo.ev_param.par3 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_3, dbo.ev_param.par4 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_4, dbo.ev_param.par5 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_5, dbo.ev_param.par6 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_6, dbo.ev_param.par7 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_7, dbo.ev_param.par8 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_8, dbo.ev_param.par9 AS GNRL_EA_PARAM_9, dbo.ev_event.loc_id AS GNRL_EA_ID, CASE WHEN v_hosts_and_slaves.nId IS NULL AND ISNULL(dbo.ev_event.deadline, GETUTCDATE()) < GETUTCDATE() THEN NULL ELSE ISNULL(dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.strDisplayName, dbo.ev_event.hostname) END "hostdn", dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nGroup AS group_id, dbo.ev_event.task_old_state, dbo.ev_event.task_new_state, dbo.ev_event.task_display_name, dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nId AS nHostId, dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nStatus AS nHostStatus, dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.strWinHostName AS host_winhostname, dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nIpAddress AS nHstIpAddress, dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nIpCon AS nHstIpCon, dbo.ev_event.event_session_number AS event_session_number, dbo.ev_event.kca_loc_id AS KLPRCI_kca_loc_id, dbo.ev_event.registration_time AS registration_time, dbo.ev_event.event_type_id AS event_type_id FROM dbo.ev_event LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves ON dbo.ev_event.nHostId = dbo.v_hosts_and_slaves.nId LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.ev_param ON dbo.ev_event.event_id = dbo.ev_param.event_id) AS v_full_event WHERE event_id > ? ORDER BY event_id
